  "texts": [
    "In intuitive physics and causal reasoning, the models managed to solve some of the given tasks and GPT-4V showed a slight match with human data.",
    "However, while they performed well in some tasks, the models did not show a conclusive match with human data for the causal reasoning experiments.",
    "Finally, in the intuitive psychology tasks, none of the models showed a strong match with human data.",
    "Thus, an appropriate answer to the question motivating our work would be 'No', or-perhaps more optimistically-'Not quite'.",
    "Although we have tried our best to give all models a fair chance and set up the experiments in a clean and replicable fashion, some shortcomings remain that should be addressed in future work."
  ],
